# Frontend (React + Vite + TypeScript + pnpm)

## Layout

```
frontend/src/
  main.tsx             # entry
  App.tsx              # router shell
  types/api.ts         # shared API response types
  lib/api.ts           # API base URL (VITE_API_URL)
  pages/Dashboard.tsx  # main dashboard, Technical Health Matrix, llms.txt block
  pages/PageDetail.tsx # deep audit signals grid
```

## Conventions

- Package manager: **pnpm** (`packageManager` pinned in `package.json`)
- Security: `.npmrc` enforces lockfile + `minimum-release-age`; never switch back to npm
- TypeScript: **strict** mode; run `pnpm typecheck` before committing
- Styling: Tailwind in TSX; global styles in `index.css` / `App.css`
- API types live in `src/types/api.ts`; use `apiUrl()` from `src/lib/api.ts`
- Peec UI is hidden when `peec_available: false` from `GET /api/health`

## Scripts

```bash
pnpm dev        # dev server :5173
pnpm build      # tsc + production build
pnpm typecheck  # strict TS check
pnpm lint       # eslint
pnpm test       # vitest
pnpm format     # prettier
```

## UI ↔ API mapping

| UI area | Endpoint |
|---------|----------|
| Domain gaps | `GET /api/gaps?domain=` |
| Roadmap | `GET /api/benchmark?domain=` |
| How to Fix panel | `POST /api/generate-fix` |
| Draft Content | `POST /api/generate-content` |
| Deep audit | `POST /api/audit` |
| Peec availability | `GET /api/health` |

